overview.en: TIME is an innovative ecological digital currency based on the practice of blockchain production relations. The value of TIME ecology is to use technology to guide the self-revolution of production relations in traditional business models, optimize business circulation methods, and return true value to the public.
overview.zh: TIME是一种基于践行区块链生产关系的，创新的生态数字货币，TIME生态的价值在于用技术引导传统商业模式中生产关系的自我革命，优化商业流通方式，让真实的价值回归大众。
